This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-mender-seeed layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

This layer is based on https://github.com/Seeed-Studio/meta-seeed-cm4

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/mendersoftware/meta-mender
  branch: kirkstone

Contributions
=============

Please the README file in the top level directory.

